<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="amuse-vt">amuse <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'mjuːz/    美 /ə'mjuːz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-entertain">1.★ <strong>给...提供娱乐 / 消遣(entertain)；逗...乐：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The children <strong>amused themselves</strong> by playing hide-and-seek games.
孩子们玩捉迷藏游戏来取乐。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>amusing /ə'mjuːzɪŋ/ adj   </p></div>